These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, april, february, november, october, august, december
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in december##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Birthday   | october | may | april | february | november | august | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
City: boston, hamburg, prague, san-francisco, miami, colone, venice
 1. the person traveling to colone is the person traveling to colone##1
 2. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
 3. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
10. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| City   | san-francisco | hamburg | colone | venice | prague | boston | miami |

