.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, domino, go, snooker, canasta, bridge
 1. the person playing go is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
 2. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
 4. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 6. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 7. the person playing domino is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person playing monopoly##7
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Game   | snooker | canasta | go | bridge | mah-jongg | domino | monopoly |

