.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
7 different pets are kept: pony, rat, chinchilla, frog, mouse, fish, hamster
 1. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the rat##7
 2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the rat##7
 5. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the frog##7
 6. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the hamster##7
 7. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
 8. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 9. the owner of the hamster is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Pet   | chinchilla | pony | frog | hamster | mouse | rat | fish |

