 2. the alhambra-smoker is not to the left of the alhambra-smoker##8
 3. the chaman-smoker is not to the right of the oliveros-smoker##8
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 5. the game-smoker is not to the right of the siglo-smoker##8
 6. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
 8. the vegafina-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the chaman-smoker is not to the right of the game-smoker##8
10. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
11. the davidoff-smoker is not to the right of the oliveros-smoker##8
12. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
13. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
14. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2      |     3      |  4  |    5    |   6   |    7    |
| Cigar   | chaman | game | alhambra | davidoff | vegafina | oliveros | siglo |

