 3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 4. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 5. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
 7. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person watching horror movies##8
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
10. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |    2     |   3   |    4    |   5    |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | horror | zombie | family | superhero | spy | thriller |

