.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-15::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, may, january, april, february, october, march
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in january##7
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |     7      |
| Birthday   | january | april | march | october | september | may | february |

