 6. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
